column5:
This is a preprint of a paper whose final and definite form will
  appear in Central European Journal of Physics. Paper submitted 31-Jan-2013;
  revised 6-May-2013; accepted for publication 7-May-2013

13 pages, 8 figures, 1 table. To appear in IEEE Transactions on
  Nanobioscience (submitted January 22, 2013; minor revision October 16, 2013;
  accepted December 4, 2013)
